					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5291471#post-4219022</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5291471/the-suicide-of-dr-daniel-f#post-4219022</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2019 19:38:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>not_a_seagull</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3009022</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>In this day and age with HTML, JavaScript, ListPages, and CSS abuse, it can sometimes be hard to remember the old adage: <em>Keep it simple, stupid.</em> The story here is great, and I honestly prefer it to <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3939">SCP-3939</a> and the other CYOA formats on the wiki because of the instant page switch and its resemblance to the old Goosebumps CYOA’s I used to read.</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
